{"tid":1485804,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「和」與「勇」，請對大家多點信任。","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:03:27.000Z","uid":101623,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"716fb77b69ab199140d2ae851c73c255c4788efe","tid":1485804,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"首先我強調<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放核彈都不割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日係維園舉牌話<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">今日不分「和」「勇」</span></strong>個位手足<br />\n真係令小妹好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知有好多人都係咁諗嫁！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但點解！！</strong><br />\n轉個頭到左10點，連登咁多PO屌人留係金鐘，仲見到勁多破壞成果論，又話人係鬼乜乜柒柒，仲見到有人話要割？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；而金鐘手足又做乜事留係個到唔走呢？大家都煲到好大，希望今日可以和理優完結，睇下條7婆點講嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇我唔係要各打50話大家都唔岩，「對與錯」永遠係事情完結先講既都係馬後炮，我係想表達更深層次既問題，會唔會係<strong>和勇兩方都對大家信任不足？</strong><br />\n<br />\n頭先見到有巴打開PO，話有位前線手足其實走緊，<span style=\"color: blue;\">但佢一路走一路喊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我明成個8月，勇武手足幫我地打左好場，幾乎每一場遊行都有下場，同時前線手足都有好多既犧牲。但你地記得<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">85大三罷</span></strong>嘛？已經有經驗證明左同一日發生太多衝突係會Spin開左個Focus，當日傳媒就報晒各區衝突，但個日罷工既成效到底係點，到而家都冇人Prove到⋯<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">勇武手足們</span></strong><br />\n可以對和理優活動有返多點既信任嗎？唔一定每一次都要有下場先＝示威。收放自如，和勇自動切換，先可以令每一場活動發揮最大效果！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一樣野我岩岩睇Live見到，覺得好唔開心。就係勁多人係到講破壞成果，又話好失望，又話叫極唔聽，<strong>但個時先10點鐘</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係好想問，到底除左170萬人出左黎，呢一刻仲有咩成果令你咁緊張會被破壞呢？可唔可以唔好又開返對人數打飛機Mode呢？<strong>重要既係條7婆會點樣回應呢170萬人既民意</strong>，而唔係170萬呢個數字啊！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">和理非手足們</span></strong><br />\n可以對前線有返多點既信任嗎？其實前線手足們好多比你地想像中成熟同有經驗，我明而家盛傳有鬼又盛咁，都冇必要過份敏感啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實我最希望既係大家都可以<br />\n更了解彼此，並且一齊成為<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和 理 勇</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>該和時和，該勇時勇</strong>就好喇～<br />\n<br />\n我再重申<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放核彈都不割</span></span></strong><br />\n大家唔好屌黎屌去啦OK？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866f86a9995423d15b89742f08546e9391726ad0","tid":1485804,"uid":266683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZfBybU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZfBybU.jpg&h=f5abe784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e68e7f4e6d366281691ca503d60564c04ba9b1bc","tid":1485804,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edb46049def1f1bff2549e0c09d14c2f38214452","tid":1485804,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"61ec042d5cea407d904d104ed94d2c1f6ca69398","tid":1485804,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e68e7f4e6d366281691ca503d60564c04ba9b1bc","tid":1485804,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"呢啲人唔講野都唔記得有佢既存在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b6d8e92cb5914582ee32ec64c90977531bfc9d","tid":1485804,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"866f86a9995423d15b89742f08546e9391726ad0","tid":1485804,"uid":266683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZfBybU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZfBybU.jpg&h=f5abe784&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>不分和勇</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29248df273df0867198c861f4872a7334311bd09","tid":1485804,"uid":67023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於有正常post出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1275c9be28fc7fb3dc5143579f41c9c14c41b4","tid":1485804,"uid":272735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"一齊走落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46e7e54ace228144605ba7bf6affc4a4a244c4c","tid":1485804,"uid":101623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"29248df273df0867198c861f4872a7334311bd09","tid":1485804,"uid":67023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於有正常post出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:52:52.000Z","msg":"我諗岩岩有啲巴打係太緊張搞到語氣重左既<br />\n希望大家而家冷靜返<br />\n可以諗下咩先係對呢場運動有用既野<img src=\"/a